         <div type="translation">
            <ab>ablanathanablanamacharamaracharamara[ch blanathanablanamacharamaracharama[ra l[a]nathanablanamacharamaracharamar anathanablanamacharamaracharama nathanablanamacharamaracharam athanablanamacharamarachara thanablanamacharamarachar anablanamacharamaracha nablanamacharamarach ablanamacharamara blanamacharamar lanamacharama anamacharam namachara amachar macha ach a unwearied Kok Kouk Koul, keep Tais, whom Tar bore, from every chill, tertian or quartan or daily or occuring on alternate days or night fever[... Öbecause I am the father- [ÖKo]k, Kouk, Koul.</ab>
